public final class BinaryOperatorExpression
extends QueryExpression
    A binary algebraic set operation. 
     expr ::= expr (INTERSECT expr)+
        | expr ('^' expr)+
        | expr (UNION expr)+
        | expr ('+' expr)+
        | expr (EXCEPT expr)+
        | expr ('-' expr)+
